data.description: Welcome to 2637 S. 11th Street in South Philly.  This 3 bedroom 1 1/2 bath home is waiting for your personal touches to make this house your home. You will enter into a brightly lit enclosed porch ready for your morning coffee to start your day. Next you will enter the Living Room/Dining Room area featuring hardwood flooring, bay window, ceiling fan and lots of room for entertaining.  The eat-in kitchen features vinyl-tiled flooring and lots of cabinets, and the included refrigerator. Beyond the kitchen is the rare first floor large laundry room with its included washer and dryer. All appliances are offered in as is condition. Beyond the laundry room is the sizable fenced back yard with deck flooring for your extended entertaining. Upstairs you will find three sizable bedrooms and one full bath. The upper level hall boasts hardwood flooring.  The large basement is finished and features a half bath. The rear of the basement is unfinished housing the HVAC and has plenty of additional room for storage. The HVAC system is brand new, just installed on 08/14/2023. A One Year Home Warranty is offered to the buyer. This is a must see in a very desirable neighborhood. Within walking distance to East Passyunk Ave., the Broad Street subway and the Sports Complex.
